Package au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.comparison

Interface Comparable

All Superinterfaces:
Equatable
All Known Subinterfaces:
DateTimeComparable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DateCollection, DateTimeCollection, DecimalCollection, EmptyCollection, IntegerCollection, StringCollection, TimeCollection
public interface Comparable extends Equatable
Describes a set of methods that can be used to compare Collection objects with an order to other paths, e.g. determining which is greater than the other.
Author:
John Grimes, Piotr Szul
